# Environment variables — example template
#
# The Hounds of Cuchulain website is a fully static site (HTML/CSS/JS, no
# backend, no build step), so the SITE itself needs NO environment variables.
#
# A real `.env` exists in this repo but is a git-ignored leftover from the
# original project scaffold — it is not required to build, run, or deploy the
# site. If you ever add a service (e.g. a contact-form backend or analytics),
# list the variable NAMES here (never the real values) and keep the real
# values in `.env`, which is git-ignored.
#
# Example (placeholder — not currently used):
# CONTACT_FORM_ENDPOINT=
